{"tid":927973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實毒撚真係好撚慘！","createTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:23.000Z","uid":189683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"011332eb484156a884e3a3e03aeb42383a731385","tid":927973,"uid":189683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"頭先坐地鐵去九龍塘，正前方企左對情侶係到，條仔一路攬住條女一路掃佢條腰，再對住我笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩啫！有女大撚哂咩？唔洗係我面前表演丫？<br />\n心諗:吊！係就揸撚埋條女啦！<br />\n<br />\n點知佢真係係到逗條女波邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咁撚大個仔，波餅都未食過一塊，啲死mk仔就一堆二堆閪咁比佢屌⋯⋯呢個世界公平咩？？<br />\n我都係想有條女姐！等左24年，一個都無！<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節應該組個毒撚團去攝哂班狗男女鏡！<br />\n毒撚起義，由今年做起！建議兄弟去海港城或1881同利東街攝鏡！"},{"pid":"901e5da1bb2a53e42ee2fd918f2019e5784fd44d","tid":927973,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"你攝埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8232fc1879dca495c74e96e6d3de2ceb7391f0","tid":927973,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s